        "related_files": [
          "src/lib/utils/github.ts",
          "src/lib/types/index.ts"
        ],
        "evidence": [
          "In github.ts lines 40-53, commitCount is initialized to 0 and stays at 0 if the link header is missing, the regex doesn't match, or the fetch throws. The type ProjectGitHubData.commitCount is 'number', making 0 indistinguishable from 'could not determine'. A consumer displaying commit count cannot differentiate between a repo with no commits and a failed count retrieval."
